Version:        1.0.0
Release:        13%{?dist}
Summary:        Display/filter/export information about PCI or PCI Express devices

License:        MIT
URL:            https://github.com/facebook/pcicrawler
Source0:        %{pypi_source}
BuildArch:      noarch

BuildRequires:  sed
BuildRequires:  python3-devel
BuildRequires:  python3dist(setuptools)

%description
